---
title: Extra Cheesy Beef Burger & Kumara Fries with Beetroot Relish & Fried Egg
description: See life on the bright side with these sunny-side-up burgers. Juicy beef patties are topped with melty Cheddar cheese, a
fried egg and a sweet beetroot relish. If that isn’t enough to satisfy your cravings, there’s baked kumara fries fresh out of the oven with a burger sauce for dipping.
